WEBVTT

00:00.917 --> 00:03.253
(Tessa)
In suburbia, the minute
Thanksgiving is over

00:03.294 --> 00:04.879
they're already fiending
for Christmas.

00:04.921 --> 00:08.967
Oh, Tessa! Any interest
in going caroling tonight?

00:09.009 --> 00:10.218
It's November.

00:10.260 --> 00:11.594
And by the time the first frost

00:11.636 --> 00:13.221
had coated the larch

00:13.263 --> 00:15.098
even the sanest of Chatswinians

00:15.140 --> 00:16.641
were prematurely gifting.

00:16.683 --> 00:19.769
Oh-oh, looks like somebody's
stocking was hung

00:19.811 --> 00:22.105
over the chimney with care.

00:22.147 --> 00:24.983
Dad, it's not Christmas.

00:25.025 --> 00:26.484
It's almost Christmas.

00:26.526 --> 00:27.902
Besides, there might be
something in there

00:27.944 --> 00:29.612
that you have to open
right away.

00:41.666 --> 00:44.002
What?
George, what is this?

00:44.044 --> 00:45.712
'It's your itinerary.'

00:45.754 --> 00:47.338
And I know you wanna spend time
in Manhattan

00:47.380 --> 00:50.008
and I know
you wanna get to know your mom.

00:50.050 --> 00:53.428
So I got the two of you
a package, hotel, spa services.

00:53.470 --> 00:55.722
'You guys can
go to the museum, see the tree'

00:55.764 --> 00:58.391
just spend Christmas
in the city..

00:58.433 --> 01:00.101
...hanging out together.

01:00.143 --> 01:02.020
- But what about you?
- What about me?

01:02.062 --> 01:04.022
I'll-I'll roll with Yakult.

01:05.648 --> 01:08.735
- Did I nail it?
- You nailed it.

01:08.777 --> 01:11.613
While my definition of family
was suddenly expanding

01:11.654 --> 01:14.532
Ryan Shay's was about
to be blown to smithereens.

01:14.574 --> 01:17.077
Family photo
came out real sweet.

01:17.118 --> 01:19.621
Everyone's looking real sweet.

01:19.662 --> 01:22.624
- Oh, wow, look.
- Yeah.

01:22.665 --> 01:24.292
And I just wanna say

01:24.334 --> 01:27.879
well, I-I just think
it's so darn cool that..

01:27.921 --> 01:30.924
...you know, you're as close
to them as you are.

01:30.965 --> 01:32.967
I had to be close, or I wouldn't
fit in the picture.

01:33.009 --> 01:35.178
I just love your whole attitude.

01:35.220 --> 01:39.432
I love that you don't act
like you're...you know.

01:39.474 --> 01:40.892
Better-looking
than everyone else?

01:40.934 --> 01:44.479
No, silly. Like one of us.

01:44.521 --> 01:47.065
- Homosexual?
- No.

01:47.107 --> 01:49.984
I'm adopted, too, you know.

01:50.026 --> 01:53.905
- I'm not adopted.
- Yes, you are.

01:53.947 --> 01:56.783
And I just think it's great
how you embraced your family.

01:56.825 --> 02:02.413
