- He's transforming!

02:51.754 --> 02:53.756
Lying...Lisa!

02:53.798 --> 02:54.799
Honey you're gonna catch cold.

02:54.841 --> 02:57.343
Lying Lisa! Lying Lisa the liar!

02:57.385 --> 02:59.971
- You liar! You liar! Liar!
- I'm sorry! I'm so sorry.

03:00.013 --> 03:01.055
- I love you.
- We love you, son!

03:01.097 --> 03:02.098
