03:03.766 --> 03:05.768
Drive the car, Fred!
Please! Just go!

03:05.810 --> 03:08.813
- Okay! Okay! Okay!
- Just drive the car!

03:08.855 --> 03:12.442
Yeah, drive off,
you fake, lying liars!

03:12.483 --> 03:15.403
If my family's
not really my family

03:15.445 --> 03:18.489
and I'm not really a Shay
then what's real?

03:19.741 --> 03:21.701
Is this real?

03:21.743 --> 03:24.495
Ow! That seems real!

03:25.705 --> 03:28.458
Is this real?
Ow! Oh!

03:28.499 --> 03:31.794
That seems really real, too!

03:31.836 --> 03:35.924
Maybe this garbage
isn't really garbage!

03:35.965 --> 03:37.425
[screams]

03:37.467 --> 03:39.552
'No, it is!'

03:39.594 --> 03:42.096
I guess I'm the only thing
that isn't real!

03:43.973 --> 03:46.142
