06:01.194 --> 06:03.196
I saw that. Was that a look?

06:03.237 --> 06:06.199
It's gonna be a long Christmas,
guapo.

06:09.869 --> 06:11.287
Ryan's adopted?

06:11.329 --> 06:13.623
He wasn't supposed to know!

06:13.664 --> 06:15.333
Ryan never would have found out
he was adopted

06:15.375 --> 06:17.085
