'Care for another rum ball,
Lisa?'

06:21.672 --> 06:24.133
They do dull the pain.

06:24.175 --> 06:26.135
Did you ever notice how Ryan

06:26.177 --> 06:28.805
well, he lights himself.

06:28.846 --> 06:31.057
It's like he has his own
inner light.

06:32.683 --> 06:36.187
Well, that's 'cause
Ryan isn't really a Shay.

06:36.229 --> 06:39.273
You don't Shay.

06:39.315 --> 06:42.443
